I just deleted over a dozen fraud spam messages from the last 36 hours of our channel chat, with very few chat news drops and zero channel post replies. I may consider muting the chat again like I did last August, but I will make sure to promote admins from the pool of those who do actively engage with legitimate news sharing here. Admin powers will be limited to messaging while the chat is muted, but that's all that's needed. As long as everyone is respectful, there's no need for more.

It's in consideration, not decided yet, but with current events being what they are, I may not have time to moderate the chat leading into this winter. I just wasted fifteen minutes scrolling through and reporting fraud and deleting and banning and reporting spam. Then, drafting this report took another fifteen minutes. That's half an hour of my evening, which is only a few hours long, to defend against fraud attack. To repeat, this is a volunteer news channel / chat and no one is getting paid to share news, so thanks to everyone who participates in earnest and to everyone who understands the great pains taken to provide the volunteer service.

Gonzo Journalism is among the most independent and unfiltered kind. Gonzos are under the greatest attack especially because working alone makes easier targets. Of the many gonzo journalists whose works are mirrored here, uncounted have been imprisoned, live with death threats, some have been killed or wait on death row. As funny as the word gonzo may sound to people who don't know better, it's actually quite serious, for these reasons precisely, besides the value of the eyewitnesses news censored from governments sanctioned platforms. Thanks also to telegram for making it possible. It's a bother to mute the chat and cut a line of communication with random providence, but a greater threat to leave it open to attack in my absence, should I need to devote my attention to more immediate matters, as the case may be.
